{"tid":2415080,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"警方追截一公里事隔40分鐘始拘捕 青年藏士巴拿螺絲批定罪判入更生中心","createTime":"2021-02-20T03:27:06.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-20T05:14:16.000Z","uid":44209,"like":2,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"af99343d7b8f8466b4ab662bc34450f826f66761","tid":2415080,"uid":44209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T03:27:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/S58Sh5j.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FS58Sh5j.jpg&h=00468217&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n前年11.11「黎明行動」當日，警員乘警車巡邏時懷疑有人堵路，亮起藍燈追截，駛至一公里外下車搜索，事隔40分鐘才截停一名銷售員，在其背囊搜出士巴拿等工具。主任裁判官蘇文隆早前指涉案士巴拿及螺絲批可用作扑頭，認為被告是裝備齊全前往參與三罷示威，裁定他管有工具罪成，還柙待判。蘇官今按報告建議，判被告入更生中心。<br />\n<br />\n辯方今求情指，報告內容顯示被告李家杰（20歲）不適合進入勞教中心，但建議判入更生中心。辯方指報告內容正面，被告還柙期間操行和品行良好，相信判處更生中心已有足夠阻嚇作用。主任裁判官蘇文隆就兩項控罪均判更生中心。<br />\n<br />\n辯方透露，被告打算就定罪提出上訴，申請讓被告保釋等候上訴聆訊，但蘇官否決申請，被告即時收押服刑。<br />\n<br />\n全文：<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210220/JWONQF4ENZELJJRTTP4SF3P5EU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210220%2FJWONQF4ENZELJJRTTP4SF3P5EU%2F&d=8a%2F9oMJQTUqWgqWpHd%2BbkkXxRC0ARC%2FjKSdqd%2FiyNcw%3D&h=940ff2c6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210220%2FJWONQF4ENZELJJRTTP4SF3P5EU%2F&h=820dc09c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210220/JWONQF4ENZELJJRTTP4SF3P5EU/</a>"},{"pid":"e21819314361c2b746a5f9d0e11989f4b2a73a0f","tid":2415080,"uid":269578,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T03:29:05.000Z","msg":"蘇文隆的陰莖可用作性侵 (太監法官則沒有陰莖)"},{"pid":"8e4b877d161e6ca3a998998564de6259442b8e52","tid":2415080,"uid":58630,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T03:30:14.000Z","msg":"其實鉛筆都可以殺人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c74e5fbb58369f21e6b91c4f7273aa9ca306bfd","tid":2415080,"uid":138964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T03:31:01.000Z","msg":"紅官好事傳千里<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63742b0935b536367d776d151298109af92f8181","tid":2415080,"uid":44209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T03:39:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1c44c9b25344e5c58438088490fd480b605c6a1","tid":2415080,"uid":389613,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T03:48:33.000Z","msg":"所有用普通法既地區唔該盡快同香港斷絕關系，如果唔係只會害左你既國民"},{"pid":"9517dccc9cc29f9ebfc28b7c10f953c7363cfabf","tid":2415080,"uid":19527,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8e4b877d161e6ca3a998998564de6259442b8e52","tid":2415080,"uid":58630,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T03:30:14.000Z","msg":"其實鉛筆都可以殺人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T05:14:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QQ61b01.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQQ61b01.gif&h=f2c0b1cb&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}